lead_paragraph: Espanyol goalkeeper Giedrius Arlauskis, who has conceded eight goals in his last two La Liga matches, will be out for up to a month because of injury.

headline.print_headline: Espanyol Keeper Arla Sidelined, Reprieve for Coach
